<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-GV9Z2JHX5D"></script>
    <script>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', 'G-GV9Z2JHX5D');
    </script>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Condensed:300|Roboto+Mono|Roboto:100,400,700&display=block" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
      <dialog class="audio-playback-dialog-box">
          <div class="audio-playback-title-bar">
              <div class="audio-playback-title">Cassette Audio Player</div>
              <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="audio-playback-close"
                      x="0px"
                      y="0px"
                      width="32px"
                      height="32px"
                      viewBox="0 0 32 32">

                  <g stroke="none">
                      <circle class="audio-playback-close-background" cx="16" cy="16" r="15"/>
                      <g class="audio-playback-close-foreground" transform="rotate(45 16 16)">
                          <rect x="5" y="15" width="22" height="2"/>
                          <rect x="15" y="5" width="2" height="22"/>
                      </g>
                  </g>
              </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="audio-playback-contents">
              <div class="audio-playback-instructions">
                  <p>Use an audio cable to connect the headphone jack of this computer to
                      the cassette jack of a TRS-80 machine.</p>

                  <p>Boot into Basic (answering <code class="audio-playback-cass"></code> to the “Cass?” question),
                      run the <code>SYSTEM</code> command, type
                      <code class="audio-playback-name-letter"></code>, press Enter,
                      then start audio playback below. When playback ends, type
                      <code>/</code> then press Enter.</p>

                  <p>You may have to adjust the volume below or on your computer to get the TRS-80 to properly
                      load the program.</p>
              </div>

              <audio class="audio-playback-player" controls></audio>
          </div>
      </dialog>
  </body>
</html>
